\item 35 cars are grey.

\noindent \hspace{1em}Show, by calculation, that the sector angle for grey is $25.2^\circ$.

\Answerspace[2cm]
\Marks{1}

\item 175 cars are white and 150 cars are black.

\noindent \hspace{1em}Complete the pie chart to show this information.

\Answerspace[2cm]
\Marks{2}

